Phase 2 — New Information Architecture (IA) & Layout Shell
Create a new public shell without rewriting screen internals

Implement src/layouts/PublicShell.tsx with:

Top nav (sticky, minimal)

Primary routes: Explore / Inscribe / Wallet / Docs / GitHub

Secondary: Market / Activity / Protocol

Footer: open source, protocol version, contract addresses, “immutability once sealed” statement

Key rule: existing screens remain mostly unchanged; wrap them in a shell and progressively enhance.

Routing strategy

Keep PublicApp as the public entry.

Use nested routes so the shell wraps all public screens.

Admin routes should have a separate AdminShell or stay as-is.

